        "Description": "After the fall of the I.C.A, Agent 47 finds himself alone and penniless in China.\rHe must therefore take what ever job he can get to make ends meet &amp; a criminal gang in the city of \rChongqing has offered to pay him handsomely if he can remove a thorn from their side.\rBut without the I.C.A to fund him, 47 must use whatever he can find to get the job done.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Agent Anubis.",
